443
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,680
Olá?

444
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,040
Tem alguém aqui?

445
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:14,480
Olá?

446
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:41,600
